Date: Sun, 10 May 2026 15:21:49 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat(news): 6-layer beneficiary engine (L1-L6) +
 auto-injection + T0-T4 transmission cascade

Replaces single-list beneficiary output with a 6-layer pricing transmission engine
that propagates every bottleneck through L1->L6:

  L1  Direct Scarcity Capture     - input pricing power (TSM/MU/ASML/AMAT/KLAC/GEV)
  L2  Compute Substitutes         - GPU/CPU substitution (AMD/INTC/ARM/QCOM/AVGO/MRVL)
  L3  Edge Distribution           - CDN/latency/bandwidth (AKAM/NET/CIEN/LITE/COHR)
  L4  Transmission Winners        - Sterlite-type pass-through (STL/PRY/GLW/Murata/Ibiden)
  L5  Platform Beneficiaries      - hyperscalers (MSFT/AMZN/GOOGL/META/ORCL)
  L6  Infrastructure / Efficiency - power, thermal, perf-per-watt (VRT/JCI/CARR/Delta)

Auto-injection rules (mandatory tickers per node-class):
  COMPUTE / MEMORY / GPU / HBM       -> AMD, INTC, ARM
  PACKAGING (CoWoS)                  -> AMD, AVGO, MRVL, AMZN, GOOGL, MSFT
  INTERCONNECT / NETWORK_BANDWIDTH   -> AKAM, NET, CIEN, LITE
  ENERGY / COOLING                   -> VRT, ETN, GEV, ARM (perf/watt shift)

Transmission cascade T0->T4 (per-node copy):
  T0 (now)    News / constraint emerges
  T1 (0-1Q)   Sentiment + order-flow shift
  T2 (1-3Q)   Revenue acceleration in L1/L4
  T3 (3-6Q)   Margin expansion (preform -> ASP -> EBITDA cascade)
  T4 (6-12Q)  EPS rerating cycle

NewsCard adds a collapsible 'capital flow' strip below exposure mapping:
- Collapsed: one row of L1..L6 chips with top-3 tickers each
- Expanded: per-layer stacks with rationale tooltips, leverage dot, mandatory star,
  plus the T0-T4 transmission timing block

Cache key bumped v29 -> v30.
